{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862607883,"sessionID":"ses_28657a10effeJg2rEsldi5zbr1","part":{"id":"prt_d79a8da77001IuMV305Gsdswm5","messageID":"msg_d79a8d10f001dEBAU6TP9bmPL5","sessionID":"ses_28657a10effeJg2rEsldi5zbr1","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_7604ec76637c46aaa81cdc91","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-018/README.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-018/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-018: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n2: \n3: - **Module**: pkg/agentd\n4: - **Language**: Go\n5: - **Size**: S\n6: \n7: ## Directories\n8: \n9: - `notes/` - Meeting notes and research\n10: - `src/` - Source code (not yet created)\n\n(End of file - total 10 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-018: Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n- **Module**: pkg/agentd\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n\n## Directories\n\n- `notes/` - Meeting notes and research\n- `src/` - Source code (not yet created)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-018/README.md","time":{"start":1775862607865,"end":1775862607882}}}}
